<title>USA: Health Management named in holder suit.</title>
<headline>Health Management named in holder suit.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-03-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>A shareholder lawsuit seeking class action status has been filed against Health management and some officers and directors, a law firm representing plaintiffs said Tuesday.</p>
<p>The lawsuit, filed in a federal court in Manhattan, alleges that the defendants violated securities fraud provisions by, among other things, issuing false and misleading statements about the financial health of the company.</p>
<p>It also alleges that the defendants concealed &quot;matters regarding the deteriorating busines&quot; of the company.</p>
